statements: SELECT * FROM OnlineMarketplacePerformance;
SELECT id, user_id, page_url FROM OnlineMarketplacePerformance WHERE load_time_ms > 1000;
SELECT id, user_interaction_time FROM OnlineMarketplacePerformance ORDER BY user_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM OnlineMarketplacePerformance WHERE page_url LIKE '%products%';
SELECT user_id, AVG(load_time_ms) AS avg_load_time FROM OnlineMarketplacePerformance GROUP BY user_id;
SELECT * FROM OnlineMarketplacePerformance WHERE user_id = 12345 ORDER BY load_time_ms DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT id, page_url, load_time_ms FROM OnlineMarketplacePerformance WHERE load_time_ms > 1000 AND user_interaction_time BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-02-28';
SELECT user_id, page_url FROM OnlineMarketplacePerformance WHERE page_url LIKE '%products%' ORDER BY user_interaction_time ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT id, load_time_ms FROM OnlineMarketplacePerformance WHERE load_time_ms < 500 OR load_time_ms > 2000 ORDER BY user_id, load_time_ms DESC LIMIT 20;
SELECT DISTINCT user_id FROM OnlineMarketplacePerformance WHERE page_url IS NOT NULL AND load_time_ms < 1000 ORDER BY user_interaction_time DESC LIMIT 5;

SELECT users.username, products.name, orders.quantity, transactions.amount FROM users INNER JOIN orders ON users.user_id = orders.user_id INNER JOIN products ON orders.product_id = products.product_id INNER JOIN transactions ON orders.order_id = transactions.order_id WHERE transactions.amount > 100 AND products.category = 'Electronics';
